text: Hunting Flies () is a 1969 Polish comedy movie directed by Andrzej Wajda and starring Zygmunt Malanowicz, Małgorzata Braunket, Ewa Skarzanka, Hanna Skarzanka, Józef Pieracki, Daniel Olbrychski, Julia Bratna. ==Other websites== * Category:1969 comedy movies Category:Polish comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Andrzej Wajda
title: Hunting Flies (1969 movie)
